# HUD::THEFEED_GET_LAST_SHOWN_PHONE_ACTIVATABLE_FEED_ID

## Summary
Finds the feed ID of the last (currently showing) activatable feed item

## Returns
* **INT**:
iId - The id of the last shown phone activatable feed item.
( This id is returned from all END_TEXT_COMMAND_THEFEED_POST_commands )

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns the handle for the notification currently displayed on the screen. Name may be a hash collision, but describes the function accurately.
